{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for skeleton component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomSkeletonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the skeleton component tokens you want.","","        override var colorGradientMiddle:  MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomSkeletonComponentTokensProvider: SkeletonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(skeleton: CustomSkeletonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(skeleton: CustomSkeletonComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    let skeletonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own color semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let skeletonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Since"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of skeleton","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"skeleton","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSkeleton"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SkeletonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Skeleton","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider"]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}]},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider\/init(colors:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider\/colors"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documenta